In study hall I just got so bored so I started drawing on my already ripped in two places jeans. And I love it I came home and completed it. There was a tennis meeting after classes and it was really funny because me and Larua we where drawing on the chalk board the entire time stuff like about the hokages and yaoi and yuri is awesome it was quiet amusing.

 So I kind of have a lot of homework which I am going to do right now without procrastinating another miracle! I have geometry, and two tests tomorrow so I better get studying because I am really trying this year to get good grades. Gasp its like another miracle my Rana.
